<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscription Canceled Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .email_container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: {{ shopColor }};
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 52px 59px;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Roboto", "Oxygen", "Ubuntu", "Cantarell", "Fira Sans", "Droid Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .subject {
            color: #222;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 100%;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Roboto", "Oxygen", "Ubuntu", "Cantarell", "Fira Sans", "Droid Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888888;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email_container">
        <div class="header">
            <img width="100%" src="cid:top_banner">
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p class="subject">Testing Subject: Your Subscription Has Been Canceled</h5>
            <p class="greeting">Dear {{ customerName }},</p>
            <p class="description">
                We’re reaching out to confirm that your subscription has been successfully canceled. No further payments or
                orders will be processed under this subscription.
                <br /><br />
                We truly appreciate the time you’ve spent with us and hope to welcome you back in the future!
                If you have any questions or need assistance, please don’t hesitate to reach out—we’re always happy to help.
                <br /><br />
                Thank you for being a valued part of the <b>{{ shopName }}</b> community.
                <br /><br />
                Best regards,
                <br />
                The <b>{{ shopName }}</b> Team
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 {{ shopName }}. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
